Class ArrayList<E>

java.lang.Object
ArrayList<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements maintained by this list
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, Iterable<E>, List<E>
class ArrayList<E> extends Object implements List<E>
Resizable-array implementation of the List interface. Implements all optional list operations, and permits all elements, including null.
